Anyway again where was i oh yes all about nothing realy,the world owes no one a living,yet it can wend its little fingers around some one and effect them for the rest of their lives.
It can build some one up then destroy them. Destroy them when they are built up.
We blame everyone and everything rather than life and how we have played it.
The reality is that some one once said....
"Hell is other people"
Without them our wishes would never be filled and our pains when they get shatered not be there,the lesson not learnt.
(what the hell are you on about)(damned if i know)(neither do i)

It riles them to believe;
That you perceive;
The Webb they weave ;
So keep on thinking free.

22,000 days,22,000 Nights.

That which we are we are,
That which we become we can choose.
That which happens to us we have no control.
Grasp the future firmly in an embrace, with your back up against the past.

That which is , that which i have i have, that i can not change.
The dawning of the morrow is that which is.
The light of the darkness in my head.
The feelings and emotions I have had.
They really are not all that bad.
They made me human gave me love.
That which is, that is love.

Thinking is the best way to travel.

The Angel of time. ( with apologies to Rick Wake man and H.G.Wells. and real poets)


The Angel of time is calling.
The time of our birth and our death.
When time is the limit of everything.
The meaning of all our  very breath.

The angel of time can call us.
Whenever and wherever she will.
She shows herself very rarely.
When she does we must bow to her will.

All I ask for her to wait .
To give me a little more time.
Time Till I have had a few more kisses, more time to be mine.
More time to love, more time to be, more to be me.
Grab each day and hold on to its good and bad bits,It will not come round again.Love when you can,protect that love.Do not throw it away when it truely arrives.
